data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 4 bedroom 2.5 bathrooms! with all of it's bedrooms located upstairs. As you approach the well maintain front of the home you will notice the quiet and serene neighborhood. Step inside to find newer floors installed, updated paint, custom counter tops, accent walls and much more. Step out back and enjoy the newly built deck and pergola while your family and friends enjoy the pool! Just in time as well for summer night bonfires! This house comes with so much upgraded and as if that isn't enough the owners are leaving the fridge as well so that's another expense you do not need to worry about. It is perfectly located near stores and not far from Camp Jejune and top rated schools in Onslow county! The pictures don't do this home justice! Come see it! fall in love, make an offer and make this house your home!
